briefdescription.para: This type represents the "Then" and "Else" parts of an If-Then" statement. It can also be used to specify sequential actions after an event is fired in the form. It contains form-related actions and allows nested If-Then-Else structures to further define form actions.

detaileddescription.para: This type represents the "Then" and "Else" parts of an If-Then" statement. It can also be used to specify actions after an event is fired in the form. It contains form-related actions and allows nested If-Then-Else structures to further define form actions.
